textfsm_template:
Value USER (\S+)
Value PID (\d+)
Value CPU (\S+)
Value MEM (\S+)
Value VSZ (\d+)
Value RSS (\d+)
Value TTY (\S+)
Value STAT (\S+)
Value START (\S+)
Value TIME (\S+)
Value COMMAND (.+)

Start
  ^\s*USER\s+PID\s+%CPU\s+%MEM\s+VSZ\s+RSS\s+TTY\s+STAT\s+START\s+TIME\s+COMMAND\s*$$
  ^\s*${USER}\s+${PID}\s+${CPU}\s+${MEM}\s+${VSZ}\s+${RSS}\s+${TTY}\s+${STAT}\s+${START}\s+${TIME}\s+${COMMAND}\s*$$ -> Record
